nodes.text: The E-50 Landseer was a model of repurposed Corellian shuttle used by the Alliance to Restore the Republic as ambulance ships, conveying medical and repair payloads directly on the battlefield. Its hull bore the universal red sigil, an identifier for medical equipment, vehicles and personnel.
Despite being listed as a repurposed Corellian shuttle, the Landseer more closely resembles the crewed section of Kuat Systems Engineering's Wayfarer-class medium freighter.
